item.title: About us
item.author: nicolmartinezm99@gmail.com (Anthony & Nicole)
item.description: Our names are Nicole & Anthony we live in the Greater New York City area and we live for great food and better times. We typically like to get our food from Amazon, Whole Foods or Trader Joes We’re always open to trying new things We currently use MyFitnessPal to track our macros What else do you need? Our story To start I would like to say we are just a simple young couple with big dreams.
